+Goal
+- Add Velleman LABPS PSU (LABPS3005DN) driver to libsigrok.
+
+Protocol
+- Serial: 9600/8n1
+- Terminator: literal "/n" (not CR/LF)
+- Commands: *IDN?, VSET1, ISET1, VSET1?, ISET1?, VOUT1?, IOUT1?, OUTPUT1, STATUS?
+
+Files
+- src/hardware/velleman/protocol.h,c: vpsu_cmd writes "/n", reads until "/n"; helpers for set/get.
+- src/hardware/velleman/api.c: scan via *IDN?, config get/set for V/I/OUT, list ranges.
+
